IL-10 linked to the Ig heavy chain C-terminus of anti-PD-1 antibody 7A4D, but not light chain, induced MC/9 cell proliferation robustly, exhibiting a similar EC50 as human IL-10, with an EC50 of 1000 pmol/L.
